Ghana’s Housing Deficit May Double in Ten Years, GNA Reports

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-03-31T09:56:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/ghana-s-housing-deficit-may-double-in-ten-years-gna-reports.html
Ghana ’s housing deficit, currently
at one million units, will probably double within the next 10
years,  Ghana  News Agency reported, citing Akwete Akita,
executive director of  HFC Bank Ghana Ltd. (HFC) , a mortgage provider.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
